#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/gargoyle.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 15 (natural armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 52 (7d8 + 21)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft., fly 60 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/gargoyle.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 15 (+2) | 11 (+0) | 16 (+3) | 6 (−2) | 11 (+0) | 7 (−2) |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/gargoyle.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Damage Resistances** bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical "
"attacks that aren't adamantine    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** poison    \n"
"**Condition Immunities** exhaustion, petrified, poisoned    \n"
"**Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 10    \n"
"**Languages** Terran    \n"
"**Challenge** 2 (450 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/gargoyle.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**False Appearance.** While the gargoyle remains motionless, it is "
"indistinguishable from an inanimate statue. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/gargoyle.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The gargoyle makes two attacks: one with its bite and one "
"with its claws.    \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Claws.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"5 (1d6 + 2) slashing damage.\n"
msgstr ""
